00:26:15.660 --> 00:26:17.270
"Home" is tonic.

00:26:17.270 --> 00:26:19.400
"Up the hill" is subdominant.

00:26:19.400 --> 00:26:21.600
Dominant is-- And you
know, this is a woman

00:26:21.600 --> 00:26:23.890
who was a professional musician.

00:26:23.890 --> 00:26:26.670
I don't know to what
degree she studied pedagogy,

00:26:26.670 --> 00:26:28.490
but I know something,
I don't know anybody

00:26:28.490 --> 00:26:31.900
that ever had a childhood
piano teacher like that.

00:26:31.900 --> 00:26:36.370
And the only reason she ended
up in Wyndham was her husband

00:26:36.370 --> 00:26:39.060
